\"hkgmoji\" />  咁老"},{"pid":"e4861c59b5376ab4dd96f349160875fbc76e4da9","tid":272573,"uid":10890,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-06T13:05:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>認真<br />\n呢次唔好係唔係都話人廢老<br />\n<br />\n佢地個仔又死埋<br />\n真係唔想老婆受罪 其實佢都好撚慘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過點解佢自己唔一齊死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n應該大陸有小三</blockquote><br />\n小你老母三<br />\n死五毛連二奶都唔識用"},{"pid":"5008867226ac054bb8397bc320069f750727ebea","tid":272573,"uid":36164,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-06T13:18:35.000Z","msg":"呢單真係悲劇<br />\n個仔又死咗<br />\n老婆中風<br />\n一個人獨力捱住照顧佢兩年<br />\n絕對係好辛苦嘅事<br />\n<br />\n或者會有人話可憐人自有可恨處<br />\n但有時命運嘅嘢<br />\n你係咁唔好彩都無辦法<br />\n<br />\n希望唔會再有下一單"},{"pid":"4a821d01e55e6a7206f18c40559dd2a62a933df5","tid":272573,"uid":55913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-06T14:42:17.000Z","msg":"都算good ending啦<br />\n阿婆死先<br />\n阿伯有人照顧終老"},{"pid":"a56381354e3c3cd8478c4ed6b2efa396ca17302b","tid":272573,"uid":3302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-06T14:43:12.000Z","msg":"廢老的命運"},{"pid":"40d5292f672caf500672a88ed8dc581df66462dd","tid":272573,"uid":1251,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-06T23:54:07.000Z","msg":"好慘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n難以想像阿伯當時係有幾痛苦"},{"pid":"24e2b376e4e245b6290fd1d5d2f248f2af4323f2","tid":272573,"uid":24092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-07T05:40:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>廢老，有勇氣殺人點解冇勇氣面對困難？</blockquote><br />\nOn9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  試吓你八十幾歲但係仲要照顧人睇吓你會點"},{"pid":"dfd19209614027fe3bc25afe08c785812291f8f9","tid":272573,"uid":72630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-07T05:45:53.000Z","msg":"唉...睇到個心真係好唔舒服<br />\n<br />\n香港既老人關注方面真係差到世界第尾...<br />\n阿公擔心自己老婆一直受苦，自己行走就無人理佢，寧可親手殺死佢，呢樣野對佢黎講真係最大打擊。<br />\n<br />\n自己個仔無啦啦自殺死左，對佢地已經係好傷心既事，但原來可以有更差...<br />\n<br />\n唯一可以講好既野，就係阿公係監房至少好食好住，有事一定有醫生睇"},{"pid":"0cf18ae1c28d52e252635ab00ecfd9d9e435664d","tid":272573,"uid":26385,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-07T05:47:30.000Z","msg":"好慘<br />\n反對安樂死嘅道德撚應該要長命百歲 百病纏身<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c6baefcf4b30e2cc08e697f95b197e4472ebd686","tid":272573,"uid":26385,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-07T05:48:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>廢老，有勇氣殺人點解冇勇氣面對困難？</blockquote><br />\nOn9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  試吓你八十幾歲但係仲要照顧人睇吓你會點</blockquote><br />\n佢曲啫 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"11d18215bae716c31f310ec5cb5fee8e782d6c51","tid":272573,"uid":6372,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-07T05:59:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"96d88ff30730e1af57e14ef9d6784403bd087ebe","tid":272573,"uid":92178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-07T06:26:17.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"1582d04a6a58d64b7fbb2dba0b5e0ecfb03917d2","tid":272573,"uid":98386,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-07T07:58:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>安樂死咪好囉又唔推行</blockquote><br />\n道德撚屌柒你無人性</blockquote><br />\n安樂死都無人性?</blockquote><br />\n而家搞到咁班道德撚就最開心囉</blockquote><br />\n收撚皮啦煩膠</blockquote><br />\n煩到你老母呀戇尻 唔係班死道德撚延住推行安樂死 阿伯洗唔洗親手殺老婆呀 己所不欲勿施於人呀仆街仔 鬼唔望你班道德撚個個中曬風又唔死日日攤床 到時你地就知安樂死既重要性"},{"pid":"12bfda52ae3c7844deeb0dc136a3279aa01913f2","tid":272573,"uid":29947,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-07T08:02:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d1362c1f6bdf10929b76e4575d89cdef0cee494f","tid":272573,"uid":23707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-07T22:51:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"15212273bc6957ea125b0afc06e9369360a03dfe","tid":272573,"uid":64716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-07T23:07:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咁佢自己呢？咁老坐監你估好易捱？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我諗佢冇諗過要活下去。<br />\n講真  連登仔唔係幾多個有幸  活到老都有愛。 雖然悲情，但我敬重呢老人家。"},{"pid":"89aae437253481aee45378190b278c4536f405a8","tid":272573,"uid":97814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-07T23:43:24.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}